00:34:33,477 --> 00:34:34,706
Stay calm, okay?

996
00:34:34,707 --> 00:34:36,277
(Emotional)

997
00:34:36,677 --> 00:34:38,047
He knocked down the very cone he targeted.

998
00:34:39,047 --> 00:34:40,577
- Jae Seok?
- I'll go second.

999
00:34:40,917 --> 00:34:41,976
I'll go third.

1000
00:34:41,977 --> 00:34:43,916
(9th try, Jae Seok)

1001
00:34:43,917 --> 00:34:44,987
Even just once.

1002
00:34:45,947 --> 00:34:47,457
There are two more players after me.

1003
00:34:47,987 --> 00:34:50,056
- That's the right mindset.
- Nice idea.

1004
00:34:50,057 --> 00:34:51,526
- It helps you relax.
- Let's do this.

1005
00:34:51,527 --> 00:34:52,557
No pressure.

1006
00:34:56,260 --> 00:34:57,499
- Let's do this.
- No pressure.

1007
00:34:57,500 --> 00:34:58,600
(9th try, Jae Seok)

1008
00:35:04,870 --> 00:35:07,370
- The direction was great.
- It's okay.

1009
00:35:07,640 --> 00:35:09,770
- I'll go.
- How did that...

1010
00:35:10,070 --> 00:35:11,680
Se Chan has my back.

1011
00:35:11,940 --> 00:35:13,579
- True.
- Relax.

1012
00:35:13,580 --> 00:35:14,750
Yes, relax.

1013
00:35:15,150 --> 00:35:16,579
It's time to show what I've got.

1014
00:35:16,580 --> 00:35:19,580
- Please.
- That was so close.

1015
00:35:20,220 --> 00:35:21,519
- Okay.
- This is no biggie.

1016
00:35:21,520 --> 00:35:23,960
A light kick, okay?

1017
00:35:24,420 --> 00:35:25,459
- Lightly.
- That was...

1018
00:35:25,460 --> 00:35:26,930
- too light.
- It's okay.

1019
00:35:27,530 --> 00:35:29,190
(Disappointed)

1020
00:35:29,530 --> 00:35:31,300
- Too light, but no worries.
- It's okay.

1021
00:35:31,960 --> 00:35:33,569
- Se Chan.
- How about wearing shoes,

1022
00:35:33,570 --> 00:35:34,730
- Yeon Seok?
- Se Chan.

1023
00:35:35,230 --> 00:35:36,699
- Just once...
- Put your shoes on, Yeon Seok.

1024
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:38,270
- How about wearing shoes?
- No difference.

1025
00:35:38,670 --> 00:35:39,870
I like it without them.

1026
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:40,940
(9th try, Se Chan)

1027
00:35:40,941 --> 00:35:42,010
Let's do this. Please.

1028
00:35:42,710 --> 00:35:44,079
Lightly.

1029
00:35:44,080 --> 00:35:45,109
Please.

1030
00:35:45,110 --> 00:35:48,050
(Se Chan succeeded just a while ago.)

1031
00:35:48,610 --> 00:35:49,710
Let's go.

1032
00:35:58,720 --> 00:35:59,919
That was too strong.

1033
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:01,090
Did it hit the screen?

1034
00:36:01,290 --> 00:36:02,460
You end up kicking it hard.

1035
00:36:02,830 --> 00:36:04,359
I shouldn't do a run-up.

1036
00:36:04,360 --> 00:36:05,399
(Failed the 9th try)

1037
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,630
Look at you.

1038
00:36:08,900 --> 00:36:10,000
It's not over yet.

1039
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:12,400
It's not over yet. Come on.

1040
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:15,040
We still have hope. We do.

1041
00:36:15,540 --> 00:36:17,610
- I'm sorry, Won Bin.
- We have one try left.

1042
00:36:18,010 --> 00:36:19,339
Don't give up yet, guys.

1043
00:36:19,340 --> 00:36:20,449
Is it our last try?

1044
00:36:20,450 --> 00:36:21,450
(In the end, they're on their last try.)

1045
00:36:22,610 --> 00:36:24,779
- It's slowly...
- You never know.

1046
00:36:24,780 --> 00:36:25,780
(Fail, and the uniform is gone.)

1047
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:28,850
Let me ask the kids. What do you think our problem is?

1048
00:36:29,090 --> 00:36:31,959
The good one should start by kicking one down.

1049
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:34,789
- Tell us the order we should go in.
- Yes, please.

1050
00:36:34,790 --> 00:36:36,730
- Nice.
- Discuss first.

1051
00:36:37,100 --> 00:36:38,529
- Come up with a plan.
- First.

1052
00:36:38,530 --> 00:36:39,599
- First?
- First.

1053
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:40,769
- Second.
- Second.

1054
00:36:40,770 --> 00:36:41,830
- Third, fourth.
- Third, fourth.

1055
00:36:42,470 --> 00:36:43,740
- Me?
- It's just that...

1056
00:36:44,500 --> 00:36:47,070
- Put on your shoes, Yeon Seok.
- The last because I'm bad?

1057
00:36:47,270 --> 00:36:49,140
We can tell without you saying it, Yu Chan.

1058
00:36:49,470 --> 00:36:50,639
(Yeon Seok's final practice)

1059
00:36:50,640 --> 00:36:52,610
- Kick it well.
- That's it.

1060
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:53,910
I'll kick from over here.

1061
00:36:55,050 --> 00:36:56,649
Yeon Seok, this teamwork just now.

1062
00:36:56,650 --> 00:36:58,150
(Let this happen in the real game!)

1063
00:36:58,720 --> 00:36:59,780
Don't drag it out.

1064
00:37:00,180 --> 00:37:01,589
(Se Hyeong barely fails.)

1065
00:37:01,590 --> 00:37:02,720
Se Hyeong is...

1066
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:04,890
What now?

1067
00:37:05,460 --> 00:37:06,590
Nice!

1068
00:37:07,090 --> 00:37:09,689
- What?
- All four of us hit the cone.

1069
00:37:09,690 --> 00:37:10,930
- Let's do this.
- Let's go.

1070
00:37:11,130 --> 00:37:13,059
- Stick your foot out.
- "Go" in 1, 2, 3. Okay?

1071
00:37:13,060 --> 00:37:14,129
- "Go?"
- Yes.

1072
00:37:14,130 --> 00:37:15,329
In 1, 2, 3.

1073
00:37:15,330 --> 00:37:16,770
- Go!
- Go!

1074
00:37:18,270 --> 00:37:19,670
- Is Se Chan first?
- Yes.

1075
00:37:20,410 --> 00:37:23,610
Let's do this. We should end our elementary school curse.

1076
00:37:24,410 --> 00:37:25,639
Our last try.

1077
00:37:25,640 --> 00:37:27,949
(Out of 10 total tries, they're on the last try.)

1078
00:37:27,950 --> 00:37:30,210
- Be serious about it.
- Of course. Here I go.

1079
00:37:30,620 --> 00:37:33,150
- Don't look.
- Ready. Set.

1080
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:40,989
(Last try: Se Chan, fail)

1081
00:37:40,990 --> 00:37:42,389
Why didn't it hit one?

1082
00:37:42,390 --> 00:37:46,099
(Last try: Se Chan, fail)

1083
00:37:46,100 --> 00:37:48,230
(Last try, Se Hyeong)

1084
00:37:53,470 --> 00:37:54,540
Okay.

1085
00:37:55,170 --> 00:37:56,509
Come on. Just one cone.

1086
00:37:56,510 --> 00:37:59,309
(Last try: Se Hyeong, success)

1087
00:37:59,310 --> 00:38:00,709
Just once.

1088
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:01,810
(Last try: Se Hyeong, success)

1089
00:38:02,780 --> 00:38:04,080
If only my ball had hit the cone.

1090
00:38:04,750 --> 00:38:06,180
- It's okay.
- What a bummer.

1091
00:38:06,350 --> 00:38:07,889
- Are you okay?
- Yes, I'm okay.

1092
00:38:07,890 --> 00:38:09,419
(Last try, Jae Seok)

1093
00:38:09,420 --> 00:38:10,620
I have a feeling you'll hit it.

1094
00:38:14,260 --> 00:38:15,430
End it here.

1095
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:20,000
It's okay.

1096
00:38:21,830 --> 00:38:23,000
- It's okay.
- We're doomed.

1097
00:38:23,940 --> 00:38:25,640
Don't say that. It's not over yet.

1098
00:38:26,170 --> 00:38:28,510
The kids said they were doomed when Yeon Seok hasn't kicked yet.

1099
00:38:28,770 --> 00:38:30,339
- "We're doomed."
- It's not over yet.

1100
00:38:30,340 --> 00:38:31,879
- It's not over yet. He has to kick.
- It's not over yet.

1101
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:33,179
(Today's outcome depends on Yeon Seok's foot.)

1102
00:38:33,180 --> 00:38:34,379
- But...
- Please, Yeon Shik.

1103
00:38:34,380 --> 00:38:35,580
It's your golden chance.

1104
00:38:35,950 --> 00:38:37,120
Hey, Jong.

1105
00:38:38,720 --> 00:38:41,420
Remember my shot? Those who are bad make things happen.

1106
00:38:42,090 --> 00:38:44,359
- Hey, Jong.
- This time, feel the pressure.

1107
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,419
Really?

1108
00:38:45,420 --> 00:38:46,919
- Yes, feel the pressure.
- Jong.

1109
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:49,429
- Succeed, and you'll become a hero.
- Jong!

1110
00:38:49,430 --> 00:38:52,129
- Jong!
- Jong!

1111
00:38:52,130 --> 00:38:53,700
- Jong!
- Jong!

1112
00:38:53,970 --> 00:38:55,230
- Jong!
- Jong!

1113
00:38:55,500 --> 00:38:56,730
I'll end this curse.

1114
00:38:59,170 --> 00:39:00,270
Good.

1115
00:39:00,810 --> 00:39:02,640
- That scared me.
- I thought he was kicking it.

1116
00:39:03,240 --> 00:39:04,580
I can't watch it.

1117
00:39:04,740 --> 00:39:06,740
That was nice just now. Keep it up.

1118
00:39:07,410 --> 00:39:08,650
The kids are dead serious, Yeon Seok.

1119
00:39:09,650 --> 00:39:10,750
Let's do this.

1120
00:39:11,650 --> 00:39:12,949
It's time to show what I've got.

1121
00:39:12,950 --> 00:39:14,720
(Last try, Yeon Seok)

1122
00:39:22,090 --> 00:39:23,160
He's got it.

1123
00:39:23,830 --> 00:39:24,930
He's got it.

1124
00:39:29,830 --> 00:39:31,269
(The end)

1125
00:39:31,270 --> 00:39:32,300
No.

1126
00:39:35,210 --> 00:39:37,280
- No.
- No.

1127
00:39:40,340 --> 00:39:41,480
We failed again.

1128
00:39:42,180 --> 00:39:43,180
Failed.

1129
00:39:43,181 --> 00:39:44,980
But the distance was just right.

1130
00:39:46,950 --> 00:39:48,090
No.

1131
00:39:49,750 --> 00:39:51,760
- She's taking them right away.
- That was a good kick.

1132
00:39:52,560 --> 00:39:54,260
It was the best kick yet.

1133
00:39:54,660 --> 00:39:56,590
We knocked all of them down during practice.

1134
00:39:57,530 --> 00:39:59,300
(Flopping down)

1135
00:40:01,600 --> 00:40:02,770
I'm sorry, Yu Chan.

1136
00:40:03,470 --> 00:40:04,600
Sorry.

1137
00:40:07,210 --> 00:40:08,310
Yu Chan.

1138
00:40:10,070 --> 00:40:11,180
Yu Chan.

1139
00:40:13,480 --> 00:40:15,150
- Yu Chan.
- I'm sorry.

1140
00:40:15,750 --> 00:40:17,520
- Se Hyeong was good.
- Exactly.

1141
00:40:17,820 --> 00:40:19,820
- No, we're a team.
- The tiny things...

1142
00:40:20,420 --> 00:40:22,049
We tense up.

1143
00:40:22,050 --> 00:40:23,190
I'm sorry.

1144
00:40:23,620 --> 00:40:24,759
- Oh, no.
- Is it over?

1145
00:40:24,760 --> 00:40:26,220
Do we get another chance if we beg?

1146
00:40:28,260 --> 00:40:29,530
How about we harass you?

1147
00:40:31,330 --> 00:40:32,400
I'm sorry, guys.

1148
00:40:33,060 --> 00:40:35,230
- These are nice too.
- They loved FC Barcelona.

1149
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:36,400
Here.

1150
00:40:36,401 --> 00:40:38,440
- FC Barcelona...
- We should've stopped.

1151
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:40,070
Stopped? You're right.

1152
00:40:40,200 --> 00:40:42,210
Stopping there wasn't really an option.

1153
00:40:42,510 --> 00:40:43,980
What he said...

1154
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:46,340
will haunt me for a while.

1155
00:40:48,150 --> 00:40:49,180
I feel bad.

1156
00:40:49,410 --> 00:40:50,879
- Can't I just gift those to them?
- Yu Chan.

1157
00:40:50,880 --> 00:40:52,220
Cheer up, Yu Chan.

1158
00:40:52,350 --> 00:40:54,350
Yu Chan, I took a look at the uniform earlier.

1159
00:40:54,490 --> 00:40:56,920
- It was fake.
- Really?

1160
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:58,859
Become big and buy a real one.

1161
00:40:58,860 --> 00:41:00,119
Have fun playing soccer.

1162
00:41:00,120 --> 00:41:01,189
- Don't get hurt.
- Good luck.

1163
00:41:01,190 --> 00:41:02,190
(Wishing all the best for the four players)

1164
00:41:02,430 --> 00:41:04,729
- It hurts quite a lot.
- Gosh.

1165
00:41:04,730 --> 00:41:06,229
- It was the worst.
- Se Hyeong did well.

1166
00:41:06,230 --> 00:41:07,670
- No.
- He did.

1167
00:41:07,730 --> 00:41:08,800
Well...

1168
00:41:09,300 --> 00:41:11,939
Se Chan, compared to how much you practiced...

1169
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:13,740
- I talked big.
- Right.

1170
00:41:14,610 --> 00:41:17,209
Why do you keep talking big?

1171
00:41:17,210 --> 00:41:18,439
I don't know. Why did I do that?

1172
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:19,709
(The older brother is angry at his younger brother.)

1173
00:41:19,710 --> 00:41:22,280
That dribble and using your back were useless.

1174
00:41:22,450 --> 00:41:23,779
- We should get going.
- Yes.

1175
00:41:23,780 --> 00:41:26,480
Let's check where our next Whenever Guest is.

1176
00:41:27,920 --> 00:41:29,289
- Yeon Seok.
- Why is it so long?

1177
00:41:29,290 --> 00:41:31,360
Wouldn't it be better to open it quietly in this situation?

1178
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:33,889
- Doing it enthusiastically...
- That was a bit...

1179
00:41:33,890 --> 00:41:35,490
That was like, "It's my treat today."

1180
00:41:35,660 --> 00:41:36,830
I was rash.

1181
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:39,960
- I was...
- It's part of your job.

1182
00:41:40,100 --> 00:41:41,129
That was frivolous. It's become...

1183
00:41:41,130 --> 00:41:42,170
- a habit.
- I see.

1184
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:44,169
We can grab coffee after lunch.

1185
00:41:44,170 --> 00:41:45,440
- There's an hour and a half left.
- Okay.

1186
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:46,839
Should we have lunch here...

1187
00:41:46,840 --> 00:41:47,869
- or there?
- There.

1188
00:41:47,870 --> 00:41:48,939
- There is...
- Yeonnam-dong.

1189
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:50,439
- Yeonnam-dong has many good places.
- Let's go to Yeonnam-dong.

1190
00:41:50,440 --> 00:41:51,940
- Shall we go to Yeonnam-dong?
- Okay.

1191
00:41:52,040 --> 00:41:54,110
- Walk down that road.
- Okay.

1192
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:55,610
- Take the bus?
- Let's take the bus.

1193
00:41:56,010 --> 00:41:57,010
Let's go.

1194
00:41:57,250 --> 00:41:58,749
This is so bad.

1195
00:41:58,750 --> 00:42:00,719
(Checking the bus)

1196
00:42:00,720 --> 00:42:02,049
- I was the only planning type.
- You must have been frustrated.

1197
00:42:02,050 --> 00:42:03,249
Wait, we had to take that one!

1198
00:42:03,250 --> 00:42:04,289
- Is it that one?
- That's it.

1199
00:42:04,290 --> 00:42:05,660
- That's our bus!
- Oh, no.

1200
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:09,159
Wait, we can get there.

1201
00:42:09,160 --> 00:42:11,200
(The bus they have to ride)

1202
00:42:11,400 --> 00:42:12,930
- That...
- No!

1203
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:14,230
It's gone.

1204
00:42:14,231 --> 00:42:16,699
No, it stopped at a red light. Oh, we're not getting there.

1205
00:42:16,700 --> 00:42:18,570
- Oh, gosh.
- We could have taken it here.

1206
00:42:18,840 --> 00:42:20,300
- I should have looked back.
- Gosh.

1207
00:42:21,510 --> 00:42:23,240
Here's the 7738 bus.

1208
00:42:23,370 --> 00:42:24,479
Nine minutes?

1209
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:25,480
(The next bus comes in 9 minutes.)

1210
00:42:25,481 --> 00:42:27,780
We missed the bus that was right in front of us.

1211
00:42:28,110 --> 00:42:29,610
That's too bad.

1212
00:42:29,750 --> 00:42:30,979
-Some days, - Right.

1213
00:42:30,980 --> 00:42:32,220
- it just doesn't work out.
- Right.

1214
00:42:32,350 --> 00:42:34,589
But we have another game next.

1215
00:42:34,590 --> 00:42:35,749
Right.

1216
00:42:35,750 --> 00:42:37,260
We need to get over it.

1217
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:39,060
We should decide what to eat, though.

1218
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,929
Let's look it up.

1219
00:42:40,930 --> 00:42:42,030
- Hongik University?
- On our way there.

1220
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:43,560
Near Hongik University Station.

1221
00:42:44,400 --> 00:42:45,959
- We'll just go and see.
- We'll see...

1222
00:42:45,960 --> 00:42:47,029
- when we get there.
- Yes.

1223
00:42:47,030 --> 00:42:49,700
Let's just eat whatever we see on a day like this.

1224
00:42:50,470 --> 00:42:51,569
Soup would be nice.

1225
00:42:51,570 --> 00:42:53,469
But we should still have some soup.

1226
00:42:53,470 --> 00:42:54,970
Yes, soup and noodles.

1227
00:42:55,040 --> 00:42:57,010
- Since we had sandwiches.
- Yes.

1228
00:42:57,410 --> 00:42:58,510
Are you a J-type?

1229
00:42:58,840 --> 00:42:59,940
No, a P-type.

1230
00:43:00,340 --> 00:43:01,410
You're all P-types?

1231
00:43:01,710 --> 00:43:02,710
- You are P, aren't you?
- I am.

1232
00:43:02,711 --> 00:43:04,850
But at moments like this,

1233
00:43:05,150 --> 00:43:07,790
I have a tendency to plan things.

1234
00:43:08,450 --> 00:43:09,490
We'll see.

1235
00:43:09,890 --> 00:43:10,989
You two are exactly the same.

1236
00:43:10,990 --> 00:43:12,659
- We'll eat whatever.
- Yes.

1237
00:43:12,660 --> 00:43:13,960
Eat anything that has soup.

1238
00:43:14,730 --> 00:43:15,730
(Scoffing)

1239
00:43:15,731 --> 00:43:18,459
Se Chan and I are so compatible when we travel.

1240
00:43:18,460 --> 00:43:20,260
"What do you think about this?" "Sure."

1241
00:43:20,560 --> 00:43:22,170
"No, let's go somewhere else." "Great."

1242
00:43:23,770 --> 00:43:25,599
Hey, this place looks good. What do you think?

1243
00:43:25,600 --> 00:43:28,040
- Where?
- It's Korean cuisine.

1244
00:43:28,210 --> 00:43:29,739
They serve these types of food.

1245
00:43:29,740 --> 00:43:30,740
- Like a full table.
- That looks good.

1246
00:43:30,741 --> 00:43:31,940
- A full table.
- Yes.

1247
00:43:32,080 --> 00:43:33,279
